                'TAN (Tax Deduction and Collection Account Number) (if deducting TDS/TCS):If the partnership firm is required to deduct Tax Deducted at Source (TDS) or collectTax Collected at Source (TCS)on certain payments as per income tax regulations, then a TAN is a mandatory registration number for compliance.',
